OL,5, Sugar beet farmers have the green light
OL,6, to use a banned pesticide deadly to    
OL,7, bees following a forecast that a virus 
OL,8, could sweep through their crops.       
OL,10,FEmergency authorisation to use         
OL,11,Fneonicotinoids was given in January but
OL,12,Frested on a threat level being met.    
OL,14,FSupplier British Sugar said the        
OL,15,Fpredicted infection rate was now 83% of
OL,16,Fcrop and was "historically high".      
OL,18,FDefra said the decision to approve was 
OL,19,Fnot "taken lightly" but campaigners    
OL,20,Fsaid it made "a mockery" of the ban.   
